while the data is in use,

84
00:04:16,230 --> 00:04:19,020
while the data is being processed.

85
00:04:19,020 --> 00:04:22,020
And that's what we are
gonna be talking about today

86
00:04:22,020 --> 00:04:24,477
and that's why we are here.

