124
00:06:15,930 --> 00:06:20,350
is the only one that has the
ability to process this data

125
00:06:21,570 --> 00:06:24,630
while keeping their
tax surface really low.

126
00:06:24,630 --> 00:06:26,250
Because we are processing sensitive data,

127
00:06:26,250 --> 00:06:28,293
we wanna contain it as much as we can.

128
00:06:29,940 --> 00:06:33,600
And some workloads here are
more CPU-heavy, compute-heavy

129
00:06:33,600 --> 00:06:36,390
and certain other workloads
are more maybe memory-heavy

130
00:06:36,390 --> 00:06:37,350
depending on the workload.

131
00:06:37,350 --> 00:06:40,770
So customers want flexibility
with resources as well.

132
00:06:40,770 --> 00:06:43,020
And all of these set of requirements

133
00:06:43,020 --> 00:06:45,600
need to get fulfilled while making sure

134
00:06:45,600 --> 00:06:48,183
we are keeping things easy to use.

135
00:06:49,440 --> 00:06:51,840
So these are some common
set of requirements

136
00:06:51,840 --> 00:06:53,700
that we have had to deal with when we work

