428
00:20:29,790 --> 00:20:30,990
But the mental model

429
00:20:30,990 --> 00:20:32,700
for the new capabilities we have launched

430
00:20:32,700 --> 00:20:35,280
and capabilities that have
existed like Nitro Enclaves,

431
00:20:35,280 --> 00:20:36,870
