432
00:20:36,870 --> 00:20:39,750
At build time, you get a reference hash.

433
00:20:39,750 --> 00:20:42,600
At runtime, you get a set of hashes.

434
00:20:42,600 --> 00:20:44,010
Are these two matching?

435
00:20:44,010 --> 00:20:47,940
If they match, then you
know you can share secrets.

436
00:20:47,940 --> 00:20:49,790
That's how we have established trust.

